snippet.title: ShemHaMephorash Early Access PV
snippet.description:
ShemHaMephorash will release on Steam at Friday, 9th April 2021.
Detailed update information and release & sale notifications will be posted on official Twitter and Steam, so please follow us on Twitter and subscribe to wish list on Steam.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1481720/ShemHaMephorash/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/SbookshelfTyche
